\v 19 \wj He aquí \+w que|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w os|strong="G5210"\+w* \+w doy|strong="G1325"\+w* \+w autoridad|strong="G1849"\+w* \+w para|strong="G1909"\+w* pisar \+w serpientes|strong="G3789"\+w* \+w y|strong="G2532"\+w* \+w escorpiones|strong="G4651"\+w*, \+w y|strong="G2532"\+w* \+w sobre|strong="G1909"\+w* \+w todo|strong="G3956"\+w* \+w el|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w poder|strong="G1411"\+w* \+w del|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w enemigo|strong="G2190"\+w*; \+w y|strong="G2532"\+w* \+w nada|strong="G3762"\+w* \+w os|strong="G5210"\+w* hará daño. \wj*  
