\v 10 \wj “\+w Dos|strong="G1417"\+w* hombres subieron \+w al|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w templo|strong="G2411"\+w* \+w a|strong="G1519"\+w* \+w orar|strong="G4336"\+w*; \+w uno|strong="G1520"\+w* \+w era|strong="G1519"\+w* \+w fariseo|strong="G5330"\+w* \+w y|strong="G2532"\+w* \+w el|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w otro|strong="G2087"\+w* \+w publicano|strong="G5057"\+w*. \wj*  
